The use of multi-party collaboration and feature selection could also suggest a potential fit for the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) sub-categories. Finally, the use of real-world datasets and experimentation could suggest a potential fit for the cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) sub-category.
